data.title: 1929) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Bedford Gazette Friday, July 19, 1929 page 8  MRS. EMILY PENROSE EVANS  Mrs. Emily Penrose Evans, died at Fishertown, July 11, 1929, of complications of diseases.  She was born near Fishertown, August 11, 1853, and was a daughter of Samuel and Polly (Smith) Penrose, both deceased.  About 43 years ago, she was married...
